  <brief_title>AKITA Inhaled Steroid Suspension for Inhalation (AICS) in Subjects With Asthma</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Trial to Evaluate Tolerability, Safety and Efficacy of AKITA Inhaled Steroid Suspension for Inhalation (AICS) in Subjects With Asthma Requiring Chronic Oral Corticosteroid Treatment</official_title>
  <sponsors>
